PrecisAppointment of ARTHUR MAJKUT, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a full-time member of the National Parole Board, Prairie Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of seven years; and designation of ARTHUR MAJKUT, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as Vice-Chairperson for the Prairie region of the National Parole Board to hold office during pleasure.
